Package: AgriDataTools
Type: Package
Title: Automated Statistical Analysis and Tools for Agricultural Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Faheem",
                  family = "Khan",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "2022ag94@uaf.edu.pk",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-8963-7157"))
Description: A comprehensive, high-performance suite of statistical tools 
    tailored for agricultural and plant breeding research. Provides automated 
    pipelines for analysis of variance (ANOVA) under Randomized Complete Block 
    Designs (RCBD) and Completely Randomized Designs (CRD), variability parameters 
    estimation, post-hoc multiple comparisons, multivariate analysis including 
    principal component analysis (PCA), path analysis, and genotypic clustering.
